OL,5,G1855 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe B&Bers head far north to
OL,7,     FRoss-shire, where hosts Diogo and
OL,8,     FRafael lay on a classic Scottish
OL,9,     Foffering at The National Hotel.
OL,10,     FBut there are tomato troubles and
OL,11,     Fbacon bother at brekkie.
OL,12,G1925 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FA lavatory letdown and some
OL,14,     Fquestionable prices cause concern
OL,15,     Fat Janie and Paul's 16th-century
OL,16,     Fhotel, The Black Bull Inn, in
OL,17,     FDumfries and Galloway.
