OL,5,G1955 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FDuring the week's final visit, to
OL,7,     FMorag and Jonny's Braeview
OL,8,     FGlamping in Berwickshire, the heat
OL,9,     Frises when two sets of guests fail
OL,10,     Fto see eye to eye over the
OL,11,     Fcampfire.
OL,12,G2025 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FAfter a tension-filled final
OL,14,     Fvisit, payment day promises to be
OL,15,     Fa feisty affair. When the dust
OL,16,     Fsettles, who'll win the week?
OL,17,G2100 The Emergency Ward
OL,18,     FDrs Dunne and Papson need answers
OL,19,     Ffor one of the sickest patients
OL,20,     Fthey've seen. Dr Thornhill
OL,21,     Fexamines a teenager who's in agony
OL,22,     Fafter falling off a dirt bike.
